title: Doku and De Ketelaere withdraw from Belgium´s Nations League squad
description: Manchester City’s Jeremy Doku is one of four players to withdraw from Belgium’s Nations League squad for their fixture against Italy and Israel. Doku becomes the fifth player from Pep Guardiola’s ranks to pull out from international duty this month and will not be available for Domenico Tedesco.
